snippet.title: Starting a game of Anteform
snippet.description: See how to play the retro RPG Anteform, including how to look for clues and get some basic armor and a weapon, without significant spoilers. Be sure to download the free manual for controls, game background, and hints. https://feneric.itch.io/anteform
